26
00:05:16,291 --> 00:05:19,583
Just one more week
and it's summer vacation.

27
00:05:21,666 --> 00:05:23,833
It's my mother's birthday today.

28
00:05:38,291 --> 00:05:40,583
You know what we said about that.

29
00:05:43,666 --> 00:05:45,875
The past is the past...

30
00:05:46,958 --> 00:05:48,500
...and now is now.

31
00:05:52,958 --> 00:05:54,041
Shall we?

32
00:05:58,416 --> 00:05:59,625
Come on.

33
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,875
Regina, you'll be late!

34
00:06:08,958 --> 00:06:12,875
