is visiting the plant. I just can't do it.

35
00:06:12,958 --> 00:06:16,416
No problem.
I don't have anything else to do.

36
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:19,625
-Regina!
-I really can do this more often.

37
00:06:19,708 --> 00:06:20,916
Regina!

38
00:06:27,125 --> 00:06:29,041
Where did you find this little one?

39
00:06:32,291 --> 00:06:34,875
-Looks like Gretchen.
-Nonsense.

40
00:06:37,791 --> 00:06:39,625
Regina, where are you?

41
00:06:40,791 --> 00:06:42,250
Listen.

42
00:06:42,958 --> 00:06:45,125
I actually wanted to talk to you.

43
00:06:46,166 --> 00:06:49,291
There's something I have to tell you.

44
00:06:51,291 --> 00:06:53,041
Hi, Grandpa. Can we go?

45
00:06:55,708 --> 00:06:57,916
No need to say bye. No problem!

46
00:06:58,791 --> 00:07:00,291
You wanted to tell me something?

47
00:07:04,333 --> 00:07:05,750
Never mind.

48
00:07:06,791 --> 00:07:08,083
All right. See you later.

